snippet: DeAnthony Thomas returned the opening kickoff 94 yards for the first of his two touchdowns as Oregon beat Kansas State in the Fiesta Bowl.
abstract: Oregon beats Kansas State, 35-17, in the Fiesta Bowl.
lead_paragraph: DeAnthony Thomas returned the opening kickoff 94 yards for the first of his two touchdowns as Oregon beat Kansas State in the Fiesta Bowl.
